  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "马卡洛夫 PM(t) 9x18PM 手枪",
      "en": "Makarov PM (t) 9x18PM pistol"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "PM（t）",
      "en": "PM (t)"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "这款具有传奇色彩的PM手枪带有延长枪管和抑制器安装螺纹。一些人声称这款手枪仅在保加利亚少量生产，另一部分人坚持认为是在东德生产，有些人甚至认为它是手工改造升级的产品。而至于这枪最后怎么跑到诺文斯克地区来的，还是问鬼去吧。",
      "en": "A semi-mythical Makarov pistol with an extended threaded barrel for equipping a sound suppressor. Some claim it was a limited production series manufactured in Bulgaria, whilst others insist on it being East German, or even a handcrafted upgrade. As for how it ended up in the Norvinsk region, no living soul could tell you now."
    },
